1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,460
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:55,932 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 3=

11
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:00,640
Stop!

12
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:05,920
Uncle Hai?

13
00:01:06,346 --> 00:01:07,840
(Lin Hai, Little Brother of Lin Rong)

14
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:08,760
(Lin Hai, Little Brother of Lin Rong)
Who is this guy?

15
00:01:10,359 --> 00:01:12,120
He's the one I brought
to treat my dad.

16
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:13,920
Treat him?

17
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:16,719
We don't need outsiders meddling.

18
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,560
What I decide is final.

19
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,120
No need for you to worry.

20
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,480
Uncle Hai, please leave.

21
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:25,920
Alright.

22
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:28,239
I won't waste words with you.

23
00:01:28,519 --> 00:01:29,560
I invited Ye Tianmiao,

24
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:32,439
the Medical Saint of Fan City,
to treat him.

25
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:34,480
(Ye Tianmiao, Medical Saint)
Can't say no now, huh?

26
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:35,411
(Ye Tianmiao, Medical Saint)

27
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,000
Mr. Ye?

28
00:01:38,599 --> 00:01:39,680
(These two...)

29
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:43,079
I just came out of seclusion

30
00:01:43,079 --> 00:01:44,879
and heard that Rong is seriously ill.

31
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:46,359
so I came right away.

32
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:51,079
Since someone's already treating him,

33
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:54,319
I'll observe for now.

34
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,519
That won't do!

35
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:57,599
How's my dad really doing?

36
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:58,920
Lin Ningxue!

37
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,879
Are you really gonna

38
00:02:01,159 --> 00:02:03,319
put your dad's life
in the hands of this unknown guy?

39
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,560
I've made up my mind.

40
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,719
If Su Wubing can't cure my dad,

41
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:09,120
I'll take responsibility.

42
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,759
Take responsibility?

43
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,719
What makes you so confident?

44
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,000
You ran from the wedding?

45
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,960
The Gu family will never let us off!

46
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:22,039
Everyone here knows
the Gu family is ruthless.

47
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,280
If it weren't for my dad,

48
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,840
I wouldn't have agreed to the marriage.

49
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:26,960
Nonsense!

50
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,120
Dad!

51
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:35,719
Uncle Hai, please leave.

52
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,039
Alright.

53
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,879
I'm done arguing.

54
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:45,560
If anything happens to Rong,

55
00:02:47,919 --> 00:02:48,840
You'll pay for this.

56
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,639
This poison has reached his bones.

57
00:02:57,639 --> 00:02:59,479
The Abyss Illusion is the only cure.

58
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:21,080
Break!

59
00:03:33,599 --> 00:03:35,360
(It's the power of the Immortal King...)

60
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:38,560
(My Lord, I finally found you.)

61
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:40,599
How's my dad?

62
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:48,879
Dad.

63
00:03:49,639 --> 00:03:50,159
Dad!

64
00:03:52,759 --> 00:03:54,360
What did you do to my dad?

65
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:55,879
Don't panic.

66
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:57,919
Once the black blood is expelled,

67
00:03:58,080 --> 00:04:00,199
the poison is gone.

68
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:04,080
(The Abyss Poison is lifted.)

69
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,360
Don't worry.

70
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,439
A little rest and he'll recover.

71
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:14,280
Really?

72
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:21,439
After ten thousand years,

73
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:24,160
I finally see you.

74
00:04:26,439 --> 00:04:28,480
Mr. Ye, what are you doing?

75
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:31,439
Do you... remember me?

76
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,720
Mr. Ye is the Medical Saint of Fan City.

77
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,759
How could he kneel before him?

78
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:37,680
Tianmiao?

79
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:39,319
It's me.

80
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,040
You remember!

81
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,600
It's been ten thousand years

82
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,199
since we parted.

83
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,560
(To directly call Mr. Ye by name...)

84
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:49,439
(Who exactly is Su Wubing?)

85
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,240
Mr. Ye.

86
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:54,480
Please stand up.

87
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,000
Stand up.

88
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:59,480
We can talk privately.

89
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,720
Yes.

90
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:10,079
The Herbal Order represents
the Ye family's legacy.

91
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:15,639
This legacy is meant
to help you come back.

92
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:18,639
This Order can mobilize
all Ye family's resources.

93
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,800
The Herbal Hall is also open to you.

94
00:05:22,519 --> 00:05:26,720
You can use all the treasures inside.

95
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:28,399
Mr. Ye.

96
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:30,439
This token is so precious.

97
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,639
You can't do this.

98
00:05:32,079 --> 00:05:33,439
Who exactly is Su Wubing...?

99
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:42,560
Rong still needs rest.

100
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,079
I won't bother you further.

101
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:50,519
We'll invite you to our house
another day.

102
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,279
Dad.

103
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:05,959
Dad.

104
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:06,920
Dad.

105
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,480
Ningxue.

106
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,000
What's...?

107
00:06:14,079 --> 00:06:14,879
What happened?

108
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,279
Dad.

109
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,879
You're alright.

110
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:21,240
Rest a bit more.

111
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,279
Don't move yet.

112
00:06:33,639 --> 00:06:34,439
Follow me.

113
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,920
Who exactly are you?

114
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:54,000
(She doesn't remember anything now.)

115
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:56,120
(Telling her would just cause trouble.)

116
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,199
You ruined Gu Yuanbing's wedding.

117
00:06:59,439 --> 00:07:02,079
And now the Medical Saint treats you
with such respect.

118
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:08,279
What's your goal in approaching me?

119
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,439
Ten thousand years...

120
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,879
all just to protect you.

121
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:19,560
What?

122
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:22,800
Why do you talk like
someone from a novel?

123
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,639
(I just cured the Abyss Poison.)

124
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,759
(It must've used up
too much spiritual power.)

125
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,480
You... what's wrong?

126
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,720
Su Wubing!

127
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:41,279
Su Wubing, wake up!

128
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:49,720
What secret are you hiding?

129
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,879
You're awake.

130
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,079
I...

131
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,480
I haven't thanked you for yesterday.

132
00:08:16,879 --> 00:08:18,160
You cured my dad.

133
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,199
A token of thanks.

134
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:21,879
There's five million
in the card and a villa.

135
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,040
All yours.

136
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,639
Take it.

137
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,319
I don't like owing anyone.

138
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,639
Another question.

139
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,039
You must answer honestly.

140
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:37,840
What caused

141
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:40,039
my dad's illness?

142
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,279
(Someone must've poisoned)

143
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:45,039
(Lin Rong maliciously using Abyss Poison.)

144
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,799
(And each dose was tiny)

145
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:47,799
(and hard to detect.)

146
00:08:49,559 --> 00:08:50,759
What are you thinking?

147
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,759
Someone...

148
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:56,360
poisoned your dad.

149
00:08:58,759 --> 00:08:59,559
Come in.

150
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,759
Got it.

151
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,639
(Dad's illness is cured,)

152
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:33,159
(but the Lin family's crisis isn't over.)

153
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:37,039
(Gu Yuanbing won't stop easily.)

154
00:09:38,279 --> 00:09:40,240
(I still need to stabilize
the group first.)

155
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:47,559
Where did that idiot come from?

156
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:49,120
How dare he ruin my plan?

157
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,039
Mr. Gu.

158
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:54,639
You.

159
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:55,879
Get down!

160
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:58,960
Down!

161
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:10,559
Open your mouth.

162
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:22,000
Hole in one.

163
00:10:24,559 --> 00:10:25,799
Alright, stand up.

164
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,200
Spit it out.

165
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:30,759
Mr. Gu,

166
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,600
that Su guy just does chores
in the martial hall.

167
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,879
Not even an apprentice.

168
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,240
Go check

169
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:39,279
his connection to the Lin family.

170
00:10:40,559 --> 00:10:42,440
Also, tell Lin Hai,

171
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:46,000
within a month,
get the Lin family secret formula,

172
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:49,039
or forget being the head
of the Lin family.

173
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,279
Yes.

174
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:52,039
And what's that guy called… Su...?

175
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:53,440
Su Wubing.

176
00:10:53,759 --> 00:10:54,279
Mr. Gu.

177
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:56,480
Should we teach him a lesson?

178
00:10:56,759 --> 00:10:59,600
I heard he has a sick mother.

179
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,799
A sick mother?

180
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:04,559
Alright.

181
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,039
This matter is yours.

182
00:11:06,039 --> 00:11:06,879
Do it well.

183
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:07,440
Got it.

184
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:10,360
The ball?

185
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,639
Lin Ningxue...

186
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:20,639
You.

187
00:11:20,879 --> 00:11:21,799
The Lins' secret formula.

188
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,440
And the Lin group.

189
00:11:24,039 --> 00:11:25,639
They will all be mine soon enough.

190
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,360
Go, get lost!

191
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:33,440
Boss, it's this room.

192
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,080
You!

193
00:11:36,639 --> 00:11:37,639
(Ye Xiaonuan, Doctor)
What are you doing?

194
00:11:37,639 --> 00:11:38,157
(Ye Xiaonuan, Doctor)

195
00:11:39,159 --> 00:11:39,759
You alright?

196
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:40,879
Yeah.

197
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,200
Go to the clinic for treatment.

198
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,320
This is the ward.

199
00:11:50,559 --> 00:11:52,879
We're here to find Su Wubing's mother.

200
00:11:53,879 --> 00:11:54,879
Mind your own business.

201
00:11:55,159 --> 00:11:55,759
Leave.

202
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,440
This is a hospital.

203
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,679
You can't cause trouble here.

204
00:11:59,519 --> 00:12:00,639
Trouble?

205
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:04,519
Listen, miss.

206
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,240
You probably haven't seen

207
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:08,080
how we guys make trouble.

208
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:12,879
You go first.

209
00:12:15,879 --> 00:12:16,639
Get lost.

210
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:20,240
I don't care about your relationship

211
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,080
with Su Wubing.

212
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,399
This is a hospital.

213
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,639
Su Wubing's family are my patients.

214
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:26,879
I'll say it once more.

215
00:12:26,879 --> 00:12:27,519
Leave.

216
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,879
Leave?

217
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,200
I can't touch him.

218
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,200
I can still handle you.

219
00:12:59,556 --> 00:13:03,659
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

220
00:13:03,659 --> 00:13:08,379
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

221
00:13:08,379 --> 00:13:13,259
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

222
00:13:13,259 --> 00:13:18,379
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

223
00:13:18,379 --> 00:13:22,779
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

224
00:13:22,779 --> 00:13:27,459
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

225
00:13:27,459 --> 00:13:32,859
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

226
00:13:32,859 --> 00:13:38,886
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

